{{pp-semi-vandalism|expiry=September 7, 2011|small=yes}}
{{Infobox Person
|image  = Amerigo Vespucci01.jpg
| caption     = Statue outside the [[Uffizi]], Florence.
| birth_date  = {{birth date|1454|3|9}}
| birth_place = [[Florence]], [[Republic of Florence]], in present-day [[Italy]]
| death_date  = {{death date and age|1512|2|22|1454|3|9}}
| death_place = [[Seville]], [[Crown of Castile]], in present-day [[Spain]]
