      <text xml:space="preserve">{{coord|37.971421|23.726166|type:landmark_region:GR|display=title}}
{{Infobox World Heritage Site
|Name        = Acropolis of Athena
|Image       = [[Image:Acropolis3.JPG|250px|The Acropolis of Athens, seen from the hill of the Pnyx to the west.]]
|State Party = {{GRE}}
